data.description: 4 Beds, 2 1/2bath in HSE school district is awaiting you. Family room facing South, located close by the new Geist Waterfront Park and Reservoir on a scenic lot with mature trees. Soaring two story foyer and great room with fireplace, open to the dining room, great room w/ fireplace and kitchen with breakfast nook.Private study with double doors and rec room in step-down level. Primary Suite, on its own level, with private bath and walk-in closet. Three additional secondary bedrooms. Three car garage. finished basement. Enjoy your mornings and evenings on the deck. This home offers a unique floor plan with good separation and a smart layout. Must see!
